	stopped. This Usually happens while a process is 
	waiting for I/O . 
Stopped (S) 	The process has been stopped, which typically 
	has happened to an interactive shell process, 
	using the Ctrl+Z key sequence. 
Zombie (Z) 	The process has been stopped but could not be 
	removed by its parent, which has put it in an 
	unmanageable state.

